main_text: Benefits Of MuskmelonMuskmelon is a summer fruit with a sweet taste. This fruit has high water content along with several other nutrients. The summer season demands proper hydration. Not just drinking water several fruits have also high water content which can also help in preventing dehydration. Muskmelon is also known as sweet melon. This is a refreshing fruit and many are not aware of its potential benefits. During the summer season you should consume fresh fruits on a daily basis to receive different nutrients. High water content of these fruits will also help you beat dehydration. main_text: Aside from keeping your children indoors to avoid heatstroke good nourishment is also important to keep them comfortable. Here’s what food items can be added to their diet:Muskmelon - Muskmelon like watermelon is a fantastic summer fruit to add to your child's diet because it is high in water electrolytes and vitamins.Curd - Curd which is high in calcium protein vitamins and minerals is a tasty and healthy coolant that not only keeps your child cool but also helps them grow and fight infections.Watermelon - Watermelon is one of the best fruits to keep your infant cool this summer because it contains 90% water is high in antioxidants vitamins and electrolytes and is low in calories.Cucumber - Cucumber has high water content and is high in fibre and minerals making it an ideal summer snack.Coconut water - Tender coconut water which is high in electrolytes (a mineral that helps the body maintain its water balance) and simple carbohydrates is a must-have in your child's summer diet.📞 022 2520 1157/ 25201180🌐 www.kolekarhospital.com🏥 Omprakash Arcade 2nd 3rd & 4th floor Ambedkar Garden Chembur Mumbai 71. comment:
{"1": {"comment_id": "kolekar_hospital_chembur"  "comment_text": "Aside from keeping your children indoors to avoid heatstroke  good nourishment is also important to keep them comfortable. Here’s what food items can be added to their diet:
Muskmelon - Muskmelon  like watermelon  is a fantastic summer fruit to add to your child's diet because it is high in water  electrolytes  and vitamins.

Curd - Curd  which is high in calcium  protein  vitamins  and minerals  is a tasty and healthy coolant that not only keeps your child cool but also helps them grow and fight infections.

Watermelon - Watermelon is one of the best fruits to keep your infant cool this summer because it contains 90% water  is high in antioxidants  vitamins  and electrolytes  and is low in calories.

Cucumber - Cucumber has high water content and is high in fibre and minerals  making it an ideal summer snack.

Coconut water - Tender coconut water  which is high in electrolytes (a mineral that helps the body maintain its water balance) and simple carbohydrates  is a must-have in your child's summer diet.

main_text: 🍈\\品評会メロンが食べられる！//今年のクラウンメロンマルシェでは、静岡県の品評会出品メロンをお召し上がりいただけます❗️3年ほど前に浜松支所が袋井のクラウンメロン支所に統合され、現在は袋井クラウンメロン支所のほか、「アローマメロン」ブランドとして販売する磐田支所・静南支所の3つの支所があります😊それらの支所共通の品評会に出品されるメロンは、メロンのトップオブトップ、市場価格は1万円以上にもなる流通量も少ない希少なメロンです🍈地元の飲食店やパティシエ、キッチンカーがそのメロンを原料に、そのままお召し上がりいただけるスイーツやアレンジした創作料理としてご用意させていただきます🎉◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎◻︎日時　6/19(日)10:00〜15:00(雨天決定/荒天中止)場所　クラウンメロン支所 袋井市小山219※イベント内容や出店者は変更となる場合がございます。#クラウンメロン #クラウンメロンマルシェ #クラウンメロンマルシェ101 #袋井クラウンメロン #静岡クラウンメロン #クラウンメロン支所 #品評会メロン #マスクメロン #アールスメロン #crownmelon #muskmelon#袋井 #袋井市 #静岡 #静岡県#イベント #マルシェ #メロンまつり #メロンサミット #子メロン #こめろん #特産品 #名産 #6次産業#グルメ #雑貨 #ワークショップ #ハンドメイド #縁日 #ファミリーイベント

{"1": {"comment_id": "crown_melon_caravan"  "comment_text": "🍈
\\品評会メロンが食べられる！//

今年のクラウンメロンマルシェでは、静岡県の品評会出品メロンをお召し上がりいただけます❗️

3年ほど前に浜松支所が袋井のクラウンメロン支所に統合され、現在は袋井クラウンメロン支所のほか、「アローマメロン」ブランドとして販売する磐田支所・静南支所の3つの支所があります😊

それらの支所共通の品評会に出品されるメロンは、メロンのトップオブトップ、市場価格は1万円以上にもなる流通量も少ない希少なメロンです🍈

地元の飲食店やパティシエ、キッチンカーがそのメロンを原料に、そのままお召し上がりいただけるスイーツやアレンジした創作料理としてご用意させていただきます🎉

※イベント内容や出店者は変更となる場合がございます。

main_text: Baazar wali malai kulfi abb ghar pe!#Kulfi is one of India's most popular desserts and it's simple to see why with so many diverse flavours.Kulfi has a long history dating back to the 16th century yet it has remained popular due to its distinct flavour. It resembles conventional ice cream but it is manufactured in a different method. Unlike ice cream kulfi is not churned resulting in a rich solid dessert.Musk Melon is one of the seasoning fruit which is commonly available in summer. Musk Melon is loaded with a lot of nutrients and it keeps your body cool. Water content is more in Musk Melon which helps you to keep hydrated during summer. It is good for your skin and hair and also improves your immune system. Hope you will enjoy making this recipe as much as I did making it for you!#MuskMelonKulfi #kulfiRecipe #KharboojaIcecream #KunalKapurRecipe #ChefKunal #ChefKunalKapur #SummerRecipe #IcecreamRecipe#icecream #kulfi #dessert #desserts #indiandessert #dessertofthedayMelon Malai KulfiPrep time - 15minsCooking time - 30mins(Serves - 6)Ingredients:Milk full fat (दूध) - 1ltMusk Melon diced (ख़रबूज़ा) - 400gmMelon seeds (ख़रबूज़े के बीज) - a handful (optional)Condensed Milk (कोंडेंसेड मिल्क) - 5 tbsp/95gms approxMilk (दूध) - ¼ cupCustard powder (कस्टर्ड पाउडर) - 1tbspGreen colour (हरा रंग) - a few dropsCheck out the step-by-step recipe for #MuskMelon Icecream here: https://www.chefkunalkapur.com/recipe/melon-malai-kulfi/
comment:
{"1": {"comment_id": "chefkunal"  "comment_text": "Baazar wali malai kulfi abb ghar pe!

#Kulfi is one of India's most popular desserts  and it's simple to see why with so many diverse flavours.

Kulfi has a long history  dating back to the 16th century  yet it has remained popular due to its distinct flavour. It resembles conventional ice cream  but it is manufactured in a different method. Unlike ice cream  kulfi is not churned  resulting in a rich  solid dessert.

Musk Melon is one of the seasoning fruit which is commonly available in summer. Musk Melon is loaded with a lot of nutrients and it keeps your body cool. Water content is more in Musk Melon which helps you to keep hydrated during summer. It is good for your skin  and hair and also improves your immune system. Hope you will enjoy making this recipe as much as I did  making it for you!

#MuskMelonKulfi #kulfiRecipe #KharboojaIcecream #KunalKapurRecipe #ChefKunal #ChefKunalKapur #SummerRecipe #IcecreamRecipe
#icecream #kulfi #dessert #desserts #indiandessert #dessertoftheday

Melon Malai Kulfi
Prep time - 15mins
Cooking time - 30mins
(Serves - 6)

Ingredients:
Milk full fat (दूध) - 1lt
Musk Melon diced (ख़रबूज़ा) - 400gm
Melon seeds (ख़रबूज़े के बीज) - a handful (optional)
Condensed Milk (कोंडेंसेड मिल्क) - 5 tbsp/95gms approx
Milk (दूध) - ¼ cup
Custard powder (कस्टर्ड पाउडर) - 1tbsp
Green colour (हरा रंग) - a few drops
